      <title>戴利说，美联储政策应限制到通货膨胀。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/daly-says-fed-policy-should-be-restrictive-until-inflation-falls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[旧金山联邦储备银行总统玛丽·戴利（Mary Daly）表示，政策必须保持限制，直到通货膨胀进展到更多，她预计随着时间的流逝，这一政策将继续下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/daly-says-fed-policy-should-be-restrictive-until-inflation-falls</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Feb 2025 16:10:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>第一天的IPO交易拖船威胁着下一波美国首次亮相</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/first-day-ipo-trading-flops-threaten-next-wave-of-us-debuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街热爱一个完美编排的IPO，提供了更多的股票，而这笔交易的提价上涨，以表明需求不断上升。在高潮时，新上市公司的股票在其第一个交易日流行，为市场启动了更多的首次亮相。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/first-day-ipo-trading-flops-threaten-next-wave-of-us-debuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Feb 2025 16:05:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雷蒙德·詹姆斯（Raymond James Cio）为黄金移动下降的理由</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-18/raymond-james-cio-makes-the-case-for-gold-to-move-lower-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雷蒙德·詹姆斯（Raymond James）首席投资官拉里·亚当（Larry Adam）表示，在过去两年中，黄金是一个情绪指标，而不是通货膨胀对冲，因为他解释了可能在明年推动价格降低的因素。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-18/raymond-james-cio-makes-the-case-for-gold-to-move-lower-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Feb 2025 15:57:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡塔尔计划在印度的100亿美元投资加深联系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/qatar-plans-10-billion-investment-in-india-to-deepen-ties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡塔尔将在印度投资100亿美元，并让其主权基金在南亚国家开设办事处，因为两国寻求加深双边关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/qatar-plans-10-billion-investment-in-india-to-deepen-ties</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Feb 2025 15:26:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>助手中断采访后，麦莉的加密抗辩反对反对。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/milei-s-crypto-defense-backfires-after-aide-interrupts-interview</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统哈维尔·麦利（Javier Milei）偶然发现了他在加密丑闻中的角色，在该丑闻中，他吹捧了后来坠毁的成员，后来在投资者从美国假期返回后，后果扩散到了阿根廷资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/milei-s-crypto-defense-backfires-after-aide-interrupts-interview</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Feb 2025 14:31:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行的Cipollone说，降低速度应考虑到QT</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/ecb-s-cipollone-says-rate-cuts-should-take-qt-into-account</link>
      <description><![CDATA[执行董事会成员Piero Cipollone表示，欧洲中央银行的利率决定不应忽视对货币政策的收紧影响，从而放松过去的资产购买。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/ecb-s-cipollone-says-rate-cuts-should-take-qt-into-account</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Feb 2025 14:19:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟要查看更多“灵活”的汽油储存填充到2025年之后</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/eu-to-look-at-more-flexible-filling-of-gas-storage-post-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟将与会员国合作，以便在未来几年内更灵活地对天然气存储进行更灵活的补充，以减少最近将价格提高到两年高的系统的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/eu-to-look-at-more-flexible-filling-of-gas-storage-post-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Feb 2025 14:06:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Diamondback再次以41亿美元的价格扩大了双鹰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/diamondback-expands-permian-oil-assets-in-double-eagle-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Diamondback Energy Inc.同意以约41亿美元的价格收购密切拥有的双Eagle IV Midco LLC的子公司后，将在二叠纪盆地扩展，这是北美最多产的页岩贴片中最高独立石油生产商的重要资产提升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/diamondback-expands-permian-oil-assets-in-double-eagle-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Feb 2025 11:16:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
